  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/c47bdff1f5af0948da61478d42f599d9.avif?t=1759243403\" width=521 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong><i>CODE Bunny, all combat techniques ARE movement options! </i></strong>You can cut through enemies in hand-crafted 2D environments with multiple routes as <strong>Axel </strong>and <strong>Hazel</strong>: Two characters with vastly different playstyles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/508059fa72dde3a87605cdd52f232434.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/508059fa72dde3a87605cdd52f232434.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/bc978793cad935b228426db158676b5e.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/bc978793cad935b228426db158676b5e.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/bc978793cad935b228426db158676b5e.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/fd32c705a0a95abb9f68c0e1a6648ecd.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/fd32c705a0a95abb9f68c0e1a6648ecd.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/b7df96a9805160425fff36a55da7fa84.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/b7df96a9805160425fff36a55da7fa84.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/b7df96a9805160425fff36a55da7fa84.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/c66b20240113863583a9b260f3c14c34.avif?t=1759243403\" width=723 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience <strong>7 Action-packed Stages</strong> with multiple routes that encourage replayability, and discover the fastest way to get to the goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On Planet Lumna, you will encounter many different and unique locations, such as Futuristic Metropoles, Ruins covered by Forests, Floating Cities Above the Clouds, and More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1ccbc352f47018428c5d3ce08d774660.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1ccbc352f47018428c5d3ce08d774660.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1ccbc352f47018428c5d3ce08d774660.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/23b52b2a20cc40ee41d427c0ef19bf10.avif?t=1759243403\" width=528 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the mysterious group \"<strong>Mad Bunny</strong>\" in exciting Boss Fights with unique mechanics that will test your skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform intense acrobatics and dodge bullet patterns while delivering combos to stagger bosses in different ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/0deed444d5099dd2657fd9786cffc76c.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/0deed444d5099dd2657fd9786cffc76c.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/0deed444d5099dd2657fd9786cffc76c.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/55c4ebefb7755c789e8504d36ea89154.avif?t=1759243403\" width=398 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In between Missions, you can take a breather from action with the \"<strong>Talk Room</strong>\" option, where you can sit back and relax with casual chats with your crewmates at Lagos Hyperbolics HQ - A Space Station orbiting Planet Lumna. Get to know more about them and the world they live in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/ec919dce3b53717d11342b93ef029a2e.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/ec919dce3b53717d11342b93ef029a2e.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/ec919dce3b53717d11342b93ef029a2e.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1e5bd25de8d2ecc26543946a8dc4df49.avif?t=1759243403\" width=643 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Axel</strong>, a former figure skater, and <strong>Hazel</strong>, a cunning warrior of the Xanadu Army. They now find themselves as members of the <strong>VY Space Program</strong> - A project aiming to harness the perfect energy source, Aethr, from <strong>Comet Yliaster</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/664be95f9cbe02f5334bae6228218fd1.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/664be95f9cbe02f5334bae6228218fd1.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/664be95f9cbe02f5334bae6228218fd1.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Following the sudden appearance of Mad Bunny in Lumna City, Axel and Hazel are tasked with finding out what their plans are. However, they will uncover a hidden conspiracy, as well as many secrets behind the nature of the world they live in…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness <i>CODE Bunny</i>’s intensely emotional narrative with several charming characters by playing through Story Mode!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/eea8e2285ba8106b2c364f72990c81f6.avif?t=1759243403\" width=643 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By clearing Story Mode, you can unlock <strong>Speedrun Mode</strong> and <strong>Boss Rush</strong>: Special challenges that will test your mastery of <i>CODE Bunny</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/a4dce4aa9bae2f6f4eb7c3f89dc68f25.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/a4dce4aa9bae2f6f4eb7c3f89dc68f25.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/a4dce4aa9bae2f6f4eb7c3f89dc68f25.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrun Mode</strong> takes you to every stage in the game back to back! An in-game clock will record your best time. Try to compete with your friends to find out who’s the fastest!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss Rush</strong> will take you to an <strong>alternate reality </strong>with a story diverging from <i>CODE Bunny</i>’s main narrative. Fight all bosses in the game back to back, and face an even more daunting challenge afterwards...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Get <strong>special gameplay rewards</strong> for beating the Extra Modes!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/c47bdff1f5af0948da61478d42f599d9.avif?t=1759243403\" width=521 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong><i>CODE Bunny, all combat techniques ARE movement options! </i></strong>You can cut through enemies in hand-crafted 2D environments with multiple routes as <strong>Axel </strong>and <strong>Hazel</strong>: Two characters with vastly different playstyles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/508059fa72dde3a87605cdd52f232434.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/508059fa72dde3a87605cdd52f232434.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/bc978793cad935b228426db158676b5e.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/bc978793cad935b228426db158676b5e.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/bc978793cad935b228426db158676b5e.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/fd32c705a0a95abb9f68c0e1a6648ecd.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/fd32c705a0a95abb9f68c0e1a6648ecd.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/b7df96a9805160425fff36a55da7fa84.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/b7df96a9805160425fff36a55da7fa84.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/b7df96a9805160425fff36a55da7fa84.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/c66b20240113863583a9b260f3c14c34.avif?t=1759243403\" width=723 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience <strong>7 Action-packed Stages</strong> with multiple routes that encourage replayability, and discover the fastest way to get to the goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On Planet Lumna, you will encounter many different and unique locations, such as Futuristic Metropoles, Ruins covered by Forests, Floating Cities Above the Clouds, and More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1ccbc352f47018428c5d3ce08d774660.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1ccbc352f47018428c5d3ce08d774660.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1ccbc352f47018428c5d3ce08d774660.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/23b52b2a20cc40ee41d427c0ef19bf10.avif?t=1759243403\" width=528 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the mysterious group \"<strong>Mad Bunny</strong>\" in exciting Boss Fights with unique mechanics that will test your skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform intense acrobatics and dodge bullet patterns while delivering combos to stagger bosses in different ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/0deed444d5099dd2657fd9786cffc76c.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/0deed444d5099dd2657fd9786cffc76c.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/0deed444d5099dd2657fd9786cffc76c.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/55c4ebefb7755c789e8504d36ea89154.avif?t=1759243403\" width=398 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In between Missions, you can take a breather from action with the \"<strong>Talk Room</strong>\" option, where you can sit back and relax with casual chats with your crewmates at Lagos Hyperbolics HQ - A Space Station orbiting Planet Lumna. Get to know more about them and the world they live in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/ec919dce3b53717d11342b93ef029a2e.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/ec919dce3b53717d11342b93ef029a2e.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/ec919dce3b53717d11342b93ef029a2e.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/1e5bd25de8d2ecc26543946a8dc4df49.avif?t=1759243403\" width=643 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Axel</strong>, a former figure skater, and <strong>Hazel</strong>, a cunning warrior of the Xanadu Army. They now find themselves as members of the <strong>VY Space Program</strong> - A project aiming to harness the perfect energy source, Aethr, from <strong>Comet Yliaster</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/664be95f9cbe02f5334bae6228218fd1.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/664be95f9cbe02f5334bae6228218fd1.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/664be95f9cbe02f5334bae6228218fd1.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Following the sudden appearance of Mad Bunny in Lumna City, Axel and Hazel are tasked with finding out what their plans are. However, they will uncover a hidden conspiracy, as well as many secrets behind the nature of the world they live in…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness <i>CODE Bunny</i>’s intensely emotional narrative with several charming characters by playing through Story Mode!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/eea8e2285ba8106b2c364f72990c81f6.avif?t=1759243403\" width=643 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By clearing Story Mode, you can unlock <strong>Speedrun Mode</strong> and <strong>Boss Rush</strong>: Special challenges that will test your mastery of <i>CODE Bunny</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/a4dce4aa9bae2f6f4eb7c3f89dc68f25.poster.avif?t=1759243403\" width=1170 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/a4dce4aa9bae2f6f4eb7c3f89dc68f25.webm?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303780/extras/a4dce4aa9bae2f6f4eb7c3f89dc68f25.mp4?t=1759243403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrun Mode</strong> takes you to every stage in the game back to back! An in-game clock will record your best time. Try to compete with your friends to find out who’s the fastest!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss Rush</strong> will take you to an <strong>alternate reality </strong>with a story diverging from <i>CODE Bunny</i>’s main narrative. Fight all bosses in the game back to back, and face an even more daunting challenge afterwards...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Get <strong>special gameplay rewards</strong> for beating the Extra Modes!</i></p>",
